snippet.textDisplay: For more than six years, "Rangabati" has been a daily companion—from college to the present. 🎵 Originally from Chhattisgarh, my connection to Odisha deepened my love for the song, especially as I started getting a better understanding of its lyrics. Every time Rituraj sings "Vande Utkala Janani," I get goosebumps. 🙌 Huge thanks to the entire team for creating this musical gem that's been a significant part of my journey. 🙏
snippet.textOriginal: For more than six years, "Rangabati" has been a daily companion—from college to the present. 🎵 Originally from Chhattisgarh, my connection to Odisha deepened my love for the song, especially as I started getting a better understanding of its lyrics. Every time Rituraj sings "Vande Utkala Janani," I get goosebumps. 🙌 Huge thanks to the entire team for creating this musical gem that's been a significant part of my journey. 🙏
